00:20:07,800 --> 00:20:09,600
就能夠在這個不幸的時代

517
00:20:09,600 --> 00:20:11,040
活出最有力的見證

518
00:20:11,040 --> 00:20:13,920
I'm not saying that it will be easy and smooth

519
00:20:13,920 --> 00:20:17,120
我並不是說這個過程是很容易的是很順利的

520
00:20:17,120 --> 00:20:19,600
But we can overcome with joys

521
00:20:19,600 --> 00:20:22,920
because we live in God's grace

522
00:20:22,920 --> 00:20:27,160
但是我們能夠得勝靠著神的恩典

523
00:20:27,160 --> 00:20:30,640
We can celebrate and shout together with the psalmist

524
00:20:30,640 --> 00:20:33,160
The Lord has done great thing for us

525
00:20:33,160 --> 00:20:35,640
and we are filled with joy

526
00:20:35,640 --> 00:20:39,960
我們可以和這個詩人一起慶祝和歡呼

527
00:20:39,960 --> 00:20:42,040
耶和華果然為我們行了大事

528
00:20:42,040 --> 00:20:43,280
我們就歡喜

529
00:20:43,280 --> 00:20:44,840
So brother and sister

530
00:20:44,840 --> 00:20:46,800
How we live for the God's kingdom

531
00:20:46,800 --> 00:20:50,280
is the most powerful witnesses to the gospel

532
00:20:50,280 --> 00:20:51,360
所以弟兄姊妹們

533
00:20:51,360 --> 00:20:53,080
我們如何為天國而活

534
00:20:53,080 --> 00:20:55,680
就是在這個不幸的時代中

535
00:20:55,680 --> 00:21:00,960
Some say that evangelism is very difficult today

536
00:21:00,960 --> 00:21:02,360
我們如何活呢

537
00:21:02,360 --> 00:21:05,120
就是為這個世代的福音做最好的見證

538
00:21:05,120 --> 00:21:08,400
有人說這個時代傳福音不容易

539
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:09,280
I agree

540
00:21:09,280 --> 00:21:11,120
要 我同意的

541
00:21:11,120 --> 00:21:14,280
It's like a shoe salesman arriving in a village

542
00:21:14,280 --> 00:21:16,200
that nobody wears shoes

543
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:17,880
就好像一個賣鞋的商人

544
00:21:17,880 --> 00:21:21,040
他到了一個村莊沒有人穿鞋

545
00:21:21,040 --> 00:21:23,360
You can say that selling shoes in this village

546
00:21:23,360 --> 00:21:24,800
is very difficult

547
00:21:24,800 --> 00:21:27,160
你可以說他要在這個村莊賣鞋

548
00:21:27,160 --> 00:21:29,440
太不容易了

549
00:21:29,440 --> 00:21:32,440
But if he can successfully demonstrate

550
00:21:32,440 --> 00:21:35,760
how wearing shoes can make walking easier

551
00:21:35,760 --> 00:21:39,440
allow you to walk further and prevent injuries

552
00:21:39,440 --> 00:21:45,120
His demonstration actually can make his business success

553
00:21:45,120 --> 00:21:50,400
但是他如果能夠示範給別人

554
00:21:50,400 --> 00:21:52,680
他怎麼樣穿著鞋走路

555
00:21:52,680 --> 00:21:55,040
怎麼樣能夠走得更遠

556
00:21:55,040 --> 00:21:56,280
走得更容易

557
00:21:56,280 --> 00:22:00,440
而且還不用擔心腳被刺傷

558
00:22:00,440 --> 00:22:04,760
那他就可以成功的賣掉這個鞋

559
00:22:04,760 --> 00:22:07,440
The success of his business

560
00:22:07,440 --> 00:22:09,640
is about his demonstration

561
00:22:09,640 --> 00:22:12,120
how to walk with that shoes

562
00:22:12,120 --> 00:22:18,480
他成功的賣鞋是因為他示範怎麼走路

563
00:22:18,480 --> 00:22:21,360
That's the most powerful testimony

564
00:22:21,360 --> 00:22:26,120
in this seemingly repetition and meaningless age

565
00:22:26,120 --> 00:22:30,720
這是一個非常非常有力的見證

566
00:22:30,720 --> 00:22:32,640
怎樣的為天國而活

567
00:22:32,640 --> 00:22:35,080
是我們最有力的見證

568
00:22:35,080 --> 00:22:37,640
So let me conclude with Paul's words

569
00:22:37,640 --> 00:22:42,720
in Philippians 1st chapter 27 to 28

570
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:46,760
所以我現在想用一個保羅在菲律賓書

571
00:22:46,760 --> 00:22:53,240
一章的話作為總結來互相的鼓勵

572
00:22:53,240 --> 00:22:54,680
Whatever happens

573
00:22:54,680 --> 00:22:56,440
Conduct yourself in a manner

574
00:22:56,440 --> 00:22:58,960
worthy of the gospel of Christ

575
00:22:58,960 --> 00:23:02,280
Then whether I come and see you

576
00:23:02,280 --> 00:23:04,960
or only hear about you in my absence

577
00:23:04,960 --> 00:23:08,760
I will know that you stand firm in the one spirit

578
00:23:08,760 --> 00:23:13,600
striving together as one of the faith of the gospel

579
00:23:13,600 --> 00:23:18,640
without being frightened in any way by those who oppose you

580
00:23:18,640 --> 00:23:22,440
This is the sign to them that they will be destroyed

581
00:23:22,440 --> 00:23:26,440
but you will be saved and dead by God

582
00:23:26,440 --> 00:23:28,680
經文說只要你們行事為人

583
00:23:28,680 --> 00:23:30,600
以基督的福音相襯

584
00:23:30,600 --> 00:23:33,360
叫我或來見你們或不在你們中間

585
00:23:33,360 --> 00:23:36,120
都可以聽到你們的狀況

586
00:23:36,120 --> 00:23:38,200
知道你們有同一個心智

587
00:23:38,200 --> 00:23:39,280
站立的穩

588
00:23:39,280 --> 00:23:41,840
為所信的福音齊心的努力

589
00:23:41,840 --> 00:23:44,600
凡事不怕敵人的驚嚇

590
00:23:44,600 --> 00:23:47,560
這是證明了他們沉淪

591
00:23:47,560 --> 00:23:49,720
而你們得救了

592
00:23:49,720 --> 00:23:52,360
May God be all the glory

593
00:23:52,360 --> 00:23:53,480
這都是出於神

594
00:23:53,480 --> 00:23:54,880
願榮耀歸於主

